<refsect1 id="GtkDataboxBars.description" role="desc">
<title role="desc.title">Description</title>
<para>
<link linkend="GtkDataboxBars"><type>GtkDataboxBars</type></link> is a <link linkend="GtkDataboxGraph"><type>GtkDataboxGraph</type></link> class for displaying xy-values as vertical bars which rise/drop from y=0.</para>
<para>

</para>
</refsect1>

